### How to Validate OCSP IPs

#### 1. Find the Responder URL for a Certificate
Use [OpenSSL](https://docs.openssl.org) to extract the OCSP endpoint from a specific certificate file:
```bash
openssl x509 -in certificate.crt -noout -ocsp_uri
